# CipherSQLStudio — Build Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A full-stack SQL learning platform with:
- **Backend** (Node.js + Express) — 3 API endpoints, SQL security middleware, PostgreSQL sandbox, MongoDB assignments, OpenAI hint service
- **Frontend** (React + Vite) — Monaco SQL editor, assignment list/editor pages, results table, hint card, dark-themed SCSS design system
- **Demo Mode** — Frontend works standalone with mock data when backend is unavailable

